Reviews.Title: Nice.....
Reviews.Author: Rl Shuey
Reviews.Content: Thankfully they made this, because I have a camera in a window that is only 6 Ft. from the DVR and I would have had to build my own cable if I hadn't found this 10 Ft. (i.e. no room to hide 25 Ft. of cable. The quality/workmanship of this cable seems to be good and I may be buying another one or two in the future. Recommended.
